ew around too, and that people is… Skeptical about you, but you pretend to change that soon. \n\n<i>“I-I see… Well my " + mcpronoun + ", let me present myself and my purpose in your city then. My name is Itzel, your humble missionary, and I have been sent from our holy church of our Goddess and savior Valeris, the giver of life, to rebuild the spiritual community in this city. I… Am not sure how knowledgeable you are about the scriptures, since I am aware that we started to preach the word of our Goddess here only after the war… And therefore my secondary mission is to teach about to those who want to know. Would… Y-you like to listen about it?”</i>\n\nShe looks nervous about asking you. You could just ignore her religious teachings, but you know whatever you like it or not, a church will be rebuilt in the city sooner than later, and having a say of what is established it’s critical for your quest for power. Of course, you could just be arbitrary about it, but who knows what will be the result of that.\n\n";
